org.apache.paimon.metrics

Interface MetricGroup

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMetricGroup, BucketMetricGroup, GenericMetricGroup

    @Public
public interface MetricGroup
    A MetricGroup is a named container for Metrics and further metric subgroups.

    Instances of this class can be used to register new metrics with Paimon.
